description: A brush fire is burning along northbound lanes of I-280 in San Francisco near the Monterey Boulevard onramp.
maintext: Firefighters are battling a brush fire burning along northbound lanes of I-280 in San Francisco near the Monterey Boulevard onramp.The fire is also burning close to several homes.Stay with ABC7 News on air and online for the latest developments
title: Brush fire burning along I-280 in San Francisco
